ligans.)_#',NULL,NULL,'Matt Thompson','138','3.882','£11/17/2017: You can use Serum Powder’s second ability only while it’s in your hand. If this card is in your hand, you can choose either to mulligan or to use Serum Powder’s ability. Using the ability doesn’t prevent you from taking further mulligans, and taking a mulligan doesn’t prevent you from using a Serum Powder’s ability if you happen to draw one in your new hand.£11/17/2017: Unlike a normal mulligan, Serum Powder lets you draw the same number of cards that were in your hand, not one less. If you have already taken one mulligan and your hand contains six cards including a Serum Powder, you can choose to exile those six cards and draw six new cards.£11/17/2017: The cards in your hand are exiled for the rest of the game; they aren’t shuffled back into your library if you take another mulligan. Cards exiled are always face up unless the effect that exiled them says they aren’t. Be sure to return those cards to your deck for your next game.','A','{C}','0.84','2.43','5.99',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'浆液粉末',NULL,'Sérum en poudre','Serumpuder','Polvere di Siero','血清の粉末','Pó de Soro',NULL,'Polvo de suero',NULL,'神器',NULL,'Artefact','Artefakt','Artefatto','アーティファクト','Artefato',NULL,'Artefacto',NULL,'{T}：加{1}到你的法术力池中。£若你处于能够再调度的时机，且浆液粉末在你手上，你可以将你的手牌移出对战，然后抓等量的牌。 （你除了再调度之外，也可以如此作。）',NULL,'{T} : Ajoutez {1} à votre réserve.£À chaque fois que vous pourriez déclarer un mulligan et que le Sérum en poudre est dans votre main, vous pouvez retirer votre main de la partie, et piocher le même nombre de cartes. #_(Vous pouvez le faire en plus de déclarer un mulligan.)_#','{T}: Erhöhe deinen Manavorrat um {1}.£Zu jedem Zeitpunkt, zu dem du einen Mulligan nehmen könntest und Serumpuder auf deiner Hand ist, kannst du die Karten auf deiner Hand ganz aus dem Spiel entfernen und dann genauso viele Karten ziehen. #_(Du kannst dies zusätzlich zum Nehmen eines Mulligans machen.)_#','{T}: Aggiungi {1} alla tua riserva di mana.£In qualsiasi 